                        "title": "كيف تقول “أنا لا أعرف ” وكيف تشكر الناس باللغة التركية",
                        "description": "<p style=\"direction: rtl;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">سوف تتعلم &nbsp;فى هذا الدرس كيف تقول :</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"direction: rtl;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">1.أنا لا أعرف التركية</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"direction: rtl;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">2.شكرا</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"direction: rtl;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">3.عفوا.</span></p>",
                        "lang": "arabic",
                        "image": "17-06-2020-I-dont-know-1-750x350.jpg",
                        "access": "public",
                        "created_at": "2020-06-16 12:33:46",
