                                        "text_content": "<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>الأن انظر الى النص أثناء استماعك إلى المحادثة.</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>İyi akşamlar arkadaşım,</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Haseki Hastanesi nerede?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e bilmiyorum</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Tamam.</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Teşekk&uuml;r ederim.</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Rica ederim</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></h2>",
