                                        "text_content": "<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&nbsp;biliyor musunuz ?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>هل تعرف؟</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Arap&ccedil;a biliyor musunuz ?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;هل تعرف العربية ؟</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Opera biliyor musunuz ?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>هل تعرف الأوبرا؟</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>وهكذا &hellip;</strong></span></h3>",
