                                        "text_content": "<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e bilmiyorum</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>تم شرح الجملة سابقا فى الدروس السابقة&nbsp;</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&Ouml;ğrenci misiniz?</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>هل أنت طالب؟</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&Ouml;ğrenci</span> = طالب</strong></span></h3>",
