                                        "text_content": "<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>الان انظر الى النص واستمع مرة أخرى للمحادثة</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Merhaba,</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Doktor musunuz?&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Hayır ben &ouml;ğretmenim.</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Tamam. Teşekk&uuml;r ederim.</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Rica ederim.</strong></span></h2>",
