                                        "access": "public",
                                        "text_content": "<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e bilmiyorum:</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;كلمة </strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Biliyor</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>: يعرف</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>كلمة &ldquo;</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">bil</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&rdquo; هي الجذر و تعني يعرف</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>اللاحقة &ldquo;</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">mi</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&rdquo; للنفي</strong></span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>اللاحقة &ldquo;</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">yor</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&rdquo; تدل على استمرارية الفعل .</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;اللاحقة&ldquo;</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">um</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&rdquo; تشير إلى \"أنا \"</strong></span></h3>",
