                                        "type": "text",
                                        "completed": "1",
                                        "lang": "arabic",
                                        "access": "public",
                                        "text_content": "<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Ben bilmiyorum:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;أنا لا أعرف</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Sen bilmiyorsun:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;أنت لا تعرف (غير رسمية)</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Siz bilmiyorsunuz:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;أنت لا تعرف(رسمية)</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">O bilmiyor:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;هو \\هي لا تعرف</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Biz bilmiyoruz:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;نحن لا نعرف</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Siz bilmiyorsunuz:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;أنتم لا تعرفون</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Onlar bilmiyorlar:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;هم لا يعرفون</span></strong></h3>",
