                                        "text_content": "<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">الان انظر الى النص واستمع مرة أخرى للمحادثة</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Merhaba , buraya oturabilir miyim?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Tabiki, sorun değil.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Ben Emre.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Ben Nihal.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Tanıştığıma memnun oldum.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Ben de.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">&Uuml;niversitede yeni misin?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Evet.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Nerelisin?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Pakistanlıyım.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Orda hangi dili konuşuyorsunuz?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Urduca konuşuyoruz.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Urduca bilmiyorum. T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşuyor musun?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e konuşmuyorum. Ama biraz biliyorum.&rdquo;</span></strong></h3>",
