                                        "access": "public",
                                        "text_content": "<h3 dir=\"rtl\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">الآن انظر الى النص ثم استمع مرة أخرى للمحادثة أثناء رؤية النص.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Bu telefonun camı kırıldı. Garanti s&uuml;resi doldu. Ne kadar tutar?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">200 TL.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">&Ccedil;ok fazla değil mi? Ne kadar s&uuml;rede alırım?</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Bu hafta sonuna biter.</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"rtl\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Bu telefonun camı kırıldı.</span></strong></h3>",
