                                        "type": "text",
                                        "completed": "1",
                                        "lang": "arabic",
                                        "access": "public",
                                        "text_content": "<h3><strong><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 115%; color: red;\">Ankara&rsquo;ya gitmek istiyorum</span><span lang=\"AR-EG\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"> أريد الذهاب إلى أنقرة</span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Ankara &ndash;</span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"color: #92cddc; mso-themecolor: accent5; mso-themetint: 153;\">y</span><span style=\"color: #e36c0a; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191;\"> - a</span></span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span dir=\"LTR\">&nbsp;&ldquo;Ankara&rdquo; </span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\">عاصمه تركيا</span><span dir=\"LTR\">.</span></span></strong></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;<span style=\"color: #e36c0a; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191;\">a</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\">&rdquo; </span></span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\">تلحق بالكلمه لاضافه معنى</span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast